title: Google launches paid version of YouTube
text:
Google launches paid version of YouTube 
Times Of India Thursday 22nd October, 2015 
YouTube Red builds on Google's existing music streaming service by providing ad-free access to YouTube programming, along with features such as the ability to download videos to mobile devices and have music playing in the background while using other mobile apps....
